metadata.name: Lotusblume Genesis
metadata.description:
Steampunk Girls

My nick is Lotus and I'm an avid fan of steampunk, particularly its unique blend of Victorian-era aesthetics and futuristic technology. As an artist, I've been exploring this theme through the creation of steampunk-inspired artwork featuring strong, empowered steampunk girls surrounded by intricate machinery and adorned with red flowers. Using cutting-edge tools such as DALL-E 2 and Midjourney, I'm able to bring my artistic vision to life and capture the essence of this captivating genre. Each piece is a unique expression of my love for steampunk and the beauty of red flowers, and I find great joy in immersing myself in the creative process.
